{"tid":1549252,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［聽日見！］9月8日香港人權與民主祈禱會","createTime":"2019-09-07T09:07:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T09:16:53.000Z","uid":143118,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6d667545c6eb938e266c566e77d2beb01cc0dfad","tid":1549252,"uid":143118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T09:07:30.000Z","msg":"9月8日香港人權與民主祈禱會<br />\n<br />\n明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。<br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n推啊推啊！要成個熱門都係聽日嘅祈禱會！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O0CK6bR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO0CK6bR.png&h=8a9846a3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"16ec6c4653b2f9646a285c2c57abbf710366a3df","tid":1549252,"uid":143118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T09:07:55.000Z","msg":"自推十次"},{"pid":"3fe8f162aaecb214cdcdd10cc983aada1e64f9f6","tid":1549252,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T09:07:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fc34a1568c75214f30d573549efbd220e85db376","tid":1549252,"uid":143118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T09:08:09.000Z","msg":"自推九次"},{"pid":"9030410b677e99090c0b6ce7f48541c19f2e045e","tid":1549252,"uid":143118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T09:08:20.000Z","msg":"自推八次"},{"pid":"10350cf60c70370204115b7a397b7f17ee918d0f","tid":1549252,"uid":143118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T09:08:32.000Z","msg":"自推七次"},{"pid":"22480296ba5fe9f783a11ded662d79b6d55e68f4","tid":1549252,"uid":143118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T09:08:43.000Z","msg":"自推六次"},{"pid":"19e5842983b9dd06c388a66025ad5f821bebc75c","tid":15